ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[Pigeons do not carry or transmit the disease, and parrots are not
reported to be susceptible to it. Although pigeons may be in contact
with wild birds that are susceptible to or transmit the disease, they
do not acquire the disease. - Mod.TG]
